    FileAssetBuilder.FileAssetParams, HLSAssetBuilder.HLSAssetParams, HSSAssetBuilder.HSSAssetParams, MPDAssetBuilder.MPDAssetParams
    public class AssetParams extends java.lang.Object implements IAssetParams
    A base class for the resulting Params objects which are generated by the AssetBuilders. Used in cases where a method needs to return a generic params instance which could be from any builder type.
